name: MainStreetFarmersMarket
0:
”Alexa, ask Farmers Market for information about the market.”
”How do I use EBT?”
”Tell me about a vendor.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: farmer's market
des:
Get information about the Main Street Farmers Market! Ask about the top five things you can do at the market, or about our Rain or Shine drawing. Get details about using your EBT benefits with the market vendors. Ask about the vendors, and Alexa will select one at random to tell you about. 

Also look for the Main Street Farmers Market news feed to add to your Alexa Flash briefing! It contains up-to-date information about what is happening each week at the market.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
